ca.ualberta.cs.corgFuViews

Class BrowseItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • ca.ualberta.cs.corgFuViews.BrowseItems
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IView

    public class BrowseItems
extends Activity
implements IView
    The activity that Allows users to browse through the currently available questions that are present in the AllQuestions model. The activity has a search bar where the user can search all questions (if they have internet connectivity) and can also choose how to sort the questions (regardless of network connectivity).
    Author:
    wrflemin
